@Navi_API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5219

### ========================================
### WEATHER FORECAST
### ========================================

### Get Weather Forecast
GET {{Navi_API_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

### ========================================
### CATEGORIES
### ========================================

### Lấy tất cả categories
GET {{Navi_API_HostAddress}}/api/categories
Accept: application/json

###

### Lấy category theo Id
GET {{Navi_API_HostAddress}}/api/categories/{{categoryId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Lấy category kèm danh sách products
GET {{Navi_API_HostAddress}}/api/categories/{{categoryId}}/products
Accept: application/json

###

### Tạo category mới
POST {{Navi_API_HostAddress}}/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Electronics",
    "description": "Điện tử và thiết bị công nghệ"
}

###

### Cập nhật category
PUT {{Navi_API_HostAddress}}/api/categories/{{categoryId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Electronics Updated",
    "description": "Mô tả cập nhật cho category"
}

###

### Xóa category
DELETE {{Navi_API_HostAddress}}/api/categories/{{categoryId}}
Accept: application/json

### ========================================
### PRODUCTS
### ========================================

### Lấy tất cả products
GET {{Navi_API_HostAddress}}/api/products
Accept: application/json

###

### Lấy product theo Id
GET {{Navi_API_HostAddress}}/api/products/{{productId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Lấy products theo category
GET {{Navi_API_HostAddress}}/api/products/category/{{categoryId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Lấy products đang active
GET {{Navi_API_HostAddress}}/api/products/active
Accept: application/json

###

### Tìm kiếm products theo từ khóa
GET {{Navi_API_HostAddress}}/api/products/search?term=laptop
Accept: application/json

###

### Tạo product mới
POST {{Navi_API_HostAddress}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Laptop Dell XPS 15",
    "description": "Laptop cao cấp cho doanh nhân",
    "price": 35000000,
    "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
    "isActive": true
}

###

### Cập nhật product
PUT {{Navi_API_HostAddress}}/api/products/{{productId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Laptop Dell XPS 15 Updated",
    "description": "Mô tả cập nhật cho product",
    "price": 36000000,
    "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
    "isActive": true
}

###

### Xóa product
DELETE {{Navi_API_HostAddress}}/api/products/{{productId}}
Accept: application/json

